Package: CMplotFastAnno
Type: Package
Title: CMplot-Compatible Plots with Fast Annotation Support
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("CMplot", "contributors", role = "aut"),
    person("CMplotFastAnno", "maintainers", role = "cre", email = "maintainer@example.com")
    )
Author: CMplot contributors and CMplotFastAnno maintainers
Maintainer: CMplotFastAnno maintainers <maintainer@example.com>
Description: Provides a CMplot-compatible plotting function for rectangular
    Manhattan plots, circular Manhattan plots, combined Manhattan and Q-Q plots,
    Q-Q plots, and marker density plots. The package keeps the original CMplot
    calling style while adding faster preprocessing, external annotation tables,
    cleaner top and nearby labels, display-only axis compression for extreme
    association signals, and clearer significance-line controls. The
    implementation uses only R packages distributed with base R and does not
    depend on external CRAN or Bioconductor packages.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    graphics,
    grDevices,
    stats,
    utils
NeedsCompilation: no
Collate:
    'global_variables.R'
    'plot_utilities.R'
    'annotation_utilities.R'
    'marker_density_plot.R'
    'circular_manhattan_plot.R'
    'rectangular_manhattan_plot.R'
    'combined_mqq_plot.R'
    'qq_plot.R'
    'CMplot.r'
